§7§oWarning, these get way laggier if they transfer to more than one output!

If you want to transfer from one inventory to another at high speed, and the two are not directly next to each other, you should use these! 

Place the transfer node on the inventory you want to pull from, and place transfer pipes to connect it to the inventory you want to push to.

You should not use filters, they make things laggier!
